  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink282-kilavi">
          iravukkuṟi nērnta tōḻi talaimakaṉ vantu puṇarntu nīṅkuḻi avaṉai etirppaṭṭuc colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> 
          What the confidante, who consented to the night tryst, said, having encountered the hero when he had come, united, and was about to depart.          
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink282">
<l>cāraṟ puṟatta peruṅkuraṟ ciṟutiṉaip</l>
<l>pēramar maḻaikkaṭ koṭicci kaṭiyavuñ</l>
<l>cōlaic ciṟukiḷi yuṉṉu nāṭa</l>
<l>vāriruḷ perukiṉa vāral</l>
<l>kōṭṭumā vaḻaṅkuṅ kāṭṭaka neṟiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>O man from the land where,</l>
        <l rend="space"> outdoors along the slope,</l>
        <l>even as the creeper-like girl,</l>
        <l>with large, desirous rain-eyes,</l>
        <l>drives them away</l>
        <l>from the small millet with big ears,</l>
        <l rend="space">the small grove parakeets</l>
        <l>[continue to] eat [them];</l>
        <l rend="space">[layers of] dense darkness have spread.</l>
        <l rend="space">Do not come</l>
        <l>along the path in the wilderness</l>
        <l>where tusked animals roam.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
